title: Fake News Example 1
text: This is a completely fake news article created for testing. It claims something that is not real.
subject: Politics

title: Fake News Example 2
text: Scientists have discovered a pill that makes you live for 500 years. This is not true but spreading fast.
subject: Health

title: Fake News Example 3
text: Aliens have been found living under the ocean, says a random website. There is no proof for this claim.
subject: Science
